nown although legend has it that it may be buried beneath tradd street in downtown charleston related products 0 pinopolis umc read more 00 cypress gardens read more  moncks corner depot read more 0 wampee house read more about us – citizens bank skip to main content about us personalinvestingsmall businesscommercialabout us our company our businessour strategy our vision and valuesleadership team leadership teamboard of directors diversity  inclusionour historyawards and recognitionsupplying goods  servicessupplier diversitycode of business conduct and ethics in the communitynewsroom latest news 000 reporter resources investor relations citizens financial group highlights our strategyfast facts financial information quarterly resultssec filingsregulatory filings  disclosuresannual reports events  presentationsfinancial news 0000 fixed income  capital information credit ratingscapital ratios corporate governance leadership teamboard of directors risk managementshareholder information stock informationdividend history company faqsalertscontact investor relations careers personalinvestingsmall businesscommercialabout us search our companyin the communitynewsroominvestor relationscareers go toabout ushomepage our company our businessour strategy our vision and valuesleadership team leadership teamboard of directors diversity  inclusionour historyawards and recognitionsupplying goods  servicessupplier diversitycode of business conduct and ethics in the communitynewsroom latest news 000 reporter resources investor relations citizens financial group highlights our strategyfast facts financial information quarterly resultssec filingsregulatory filings  disclosuresannual reports events  presentationsfinancial news 0000 fixed income  capital information credit ratingscapital ratios corporate governance leadership teamboard of directors risk managementshareholder information stock informationdividend history company faqsalertscontact investor relations careers close about us 